<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="slim-adj">slim <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /slɪm/    美 /slɪm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>苗条的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a slim young woman
身材苗条的年轻女子</p></div>

<h4 id="2small">2.<strong>微小的(small)；不足的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>slim chances</strong> of success
渺茫的成功机会</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>slim salary
微薄的薪水</p></div></div>